WEBVTT



00:00:02.656 --> 00:00:09.696
When you visit the Jerusalem Channel website, you can watch all our videos with closed caption subtitles.

00:00:09.824 --> 00:00:14.944
Select the closed caption logo at the bottom right corner of the video screen

00:00:14.688 --> 00:00:17.568
and select English.

00:00:26.528 --> 00:00:34.496
Our Jerusalem Channel Facebook page, you can select closed captions in English, Spanish, Portuguese, and Arabic.

00:00:37.632 --> 00:00:40.320
the Jerusalem Channel YouTube site

00:00:40.224 --> 00:00:42.784
has closed captions in English.
